==== ENTRY 6 ====
HEADWORD: Hollow
<hw>Hol"low</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To shout; to
hollo.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Whisperings and <qex>hollowings</qex> are alike to a deaf ear.</q>
