[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hollow</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 7 ====
HEADWORD: Hollow
<hw>Hol"low</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To urge or call by
shouting.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He has <qex>hollowed</qex> the hounds.</q> <rj><qau>Sir W. Scott.
